3. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY

   The Software embodies original intellectual property including but
   not limited to:

   (a) the mathematical framework known as "Matematika Hijaiyyah",
       comprising the formal mapping of 28 canonical Hijaiyyah letterforms
       to 18-dimensional integer codex vectors;

   (b) the computational unit known as "Hybit" (Hijaiyyah Hyperdimensional
       Bit Integration Technology);

   (c) the programming language known as "HC" (Hijaiyyah Codex);

   (d) the instruction set architecture known as "H-ISA" (Hijaiyyah
       Instruction Set Architecture);

   (e) the virtual machine known as "HCVM" (Hijaiyyah Codex Virtual
       Machine);

   (f) the skeleton graph interface known as "CSGI" (Canonical Skeleton
       Graph Interface);

   (g) the security system known as "HGSS" (Hijaiyyah Guarded Signature
       System);

   (h) the data format known as "HC18DC" (Hijaiyyah Codex 18-Dimensional
       Canonical);

   (i) the sealed dataset known as "HM-28-v1.0-HC18D";

   (j) all associated documentation, specifications, and design documents.

   All trademarks, service marks, and trade names are the property of
   the copyright holder.

